      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a student.\n   1. The applicant should belong to the NT/DNT (Nomadic Tribes and Denotified Tribes) category.\n   1. The applicant should be studying in a self-financed college in Gujarat.\n   1. The applicant should have passed the Higher Secondary Certificate (HSC) or equivalent examination.\n   1. The applicant’s individual and family annual income should not exceed ₹2,00,000/-.\n   1. The  Institute must be certified by the government.\n\n<br>\n\n",
